mal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">$(&#39;#identifier&#39;).modal(&#39;toggle&#39;)</pre></td></tr><tr style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Show:</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>.modal(&#39;show&#39;)</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\">手动打开模态框。</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\"><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">$(&#39;#identifier&#39;).modal(&#39;show&#39;)</pre></td></tr><tr style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 240);\"><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\"><strong>Hide:</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>.modal(&#39;hide&#39;)</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\">手动隐藏模态框。</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\"><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: