ript</strong>：您可以使用 Javscript 来启用标签页，如下所示：<pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">$(&#39;#myTab a&#39;).click(function (e) {\r\n  e.preventDefault()\r\n  $(this).tab(&#39;show&#39;)\r\n})</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">下面的实例演示了以不同的方式来激活各个标签页：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">// 通过名称选取标签页\r\n$(&#39;#myTab a[href=&quot;#profile&quot;]&#39;).tab(&#39;show&#39;)\r\n \r\n// 选取第一个标签页\r\n$(&#39;#myTab a:first&#39;).tab(&#39;show&#39;) \r\n\r\n// 选取最后一个标签页\r\n$(&#39;#myTab a:last&#39;).tab(&#39;show&#39;) \r\n\r\n// 选取第三个标签页（从 0 开始索引）\r\n$(&#39;#myTab li:eq(2) a&#39;).tab(&#39;show&#39;) \r\n</pre></li></ul><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">淡入淡出效果</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果需要为标签页设置淡入淡出效果，请添加<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>.fade</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>到每个<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>.tab-pane</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>后面。第一个标签页必须添加<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>.in</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>类，以便淡入显示初始内容，如下面实例所示：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;div class=&quot;tab-content&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane fade in active&quot; id=&quot;home&quot;&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;\r\n  &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane fade&quot; id=&quot;svn&quot;&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;\r\n  &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane fade&quot; id=&quot;ios&quot;&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;\r\n  &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane fade&quot; id=&quot;java&quot;&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;</pre><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">实例</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下面的实例演示了使用 data 属性的标签页（Tab）插件及其淡入淡出的效果：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint tryit\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n   &lt;title&gt;Bootstrap 实例 - 标签页（Tab）插件&lt;/title&gt;\r\n   &lt;link href=&quot;/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot; rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;/scripts/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul id=&quot;myTab&quot; class=&quot;nav nav-tabs&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;li class=&quot;active&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;a href=&quot;#home&quot; data-toggle=&quot;tab&quot;&gt;\r\n         W3Cschool Home\r\n      &lt;/a&gt;\r\n   &lt;/li&gt;\r\n   &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#ios&quot; data-toggle=&quot;tab&quot;&gt;iOS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n   &lt;li class=&quot;dropdown&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; id=&quot;myTabDrop1&quot; class=&quot;dropdown-toggle&quot; \r\n         data-toggle=&quot;dropdown&quot;&gt;Java \r\n         &lt;b class=&quot;caret&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;\r\n      &lt;/a&gt;\r\n      &lt;ul class=&quot;dropdown-menu&quot; role=&quot;menu&quot; aria-labelledby=&quot;myTabDrop1&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#jmeter&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; data-toggle=&quot;tab&quot;&gt;jmeter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n         &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#ejb&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; data-toggle=&quot;tab&quot;&gt;ejb&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n      &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n   &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;myTabContent&quot; class=&quot;tab-content&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane fade in active&quot; id=&quot;home&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;p&gt;W3Cschoool菜鸟教程是一个提供最新的web技术站点，本站免费提供了建站相关的技术文档，帮助广大web技术爱好者快速入门并建立自己的网站。菜鸟先飞早入行——学的不仅是技术，更是梦想。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane fade&quot; id=&quot;ios&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;p&gt;iOS 是一个由苹果公司开发和发布的手机操作系统。最初是于 2007 年首次发布 iPhone、iPod Touch 和 Apple \r\n      TV。iOS 派生自 OS X，它们共享 Darwin 基础。OS X 操作系统是用在苹果电脑上，iOS 是苹果的移动版本。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane fade&quot; id=&quot;jmeter&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;p&gt;jMeter 是一款开源的测试软件。它是 100% 纯 Java 应用程序，用于负载和性能测试。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane fade&quot; id=&quot;ejb&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;p&gt;Enterprise Java Beans（EJB）是一个创建高度可扩展性和强大企业级应用程序的开发架构，部署在兼容应用程序服务器（比如 JBOSS、Web Logic 等）的 J2EE 上。\r\n      &lt;/p&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p><br/></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结果如下所示：</p><div class=\"cover\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/tabplugin_demo.jpg\" alt=\"标签页（Tab）插件\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></div><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">方法</h2><p><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">.$().tab</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">：该方法可以激活标签页元素和内容容器。标签页需要用一个<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">data-target</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>或者一个指向 DOM 中容器节点的<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">href</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">。</span></p><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;ul class=&quot;nav nav-tabs&quot; id=&quot;myTab&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;li class=&quot;active&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#identifier&quot; data-toggle=&quot;tab&quot;&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n  .....\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;tab-content&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane active&quot; id=&quot;home&quot;&gt;...&lt;/div&gt;\r\n  .....\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;script&gt;\r\n  $(function () {\r\n    $(&#39;#myTab a:last&#39;).tab(&#39;show&#39;)\r\n  })\r\n&lt;/script&gt;</pre><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">实例</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下面的实例演示了标签页（Tab）插件方法<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>.tab</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>的用法。在本实例中，第二个标签页<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><em>iOS</em><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>是激活的：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint tryit\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n   &lt;title&gt;Bootstrap 实例 - 标签页（Tab）插件方法&lt;/title&gt;\r\n   &lt;link href=&quot;/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot; rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;/scripts/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ul id=&quot;myTab&quot; class=&quot;nav nav-tabs&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;li class=&quot;active&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#home&quot; data-toggle=&quot;tab&quot;&gt;\r\n      W3Cschool Home&lt;/a&gt;\r\n   &lt;/li&gt;\r\n   &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#ios&quot; data-toggle=&quot;tab&quot;&gt;iOS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n   &lt;li class=&quot;dropdown&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; id=&quot;myTabDrop1&quot; class=&quot;dropdown-toggle&quot; \r\n         data-toggle=&quot;dropdown&quot;&gt;Java &lt;b class=&quot;caret&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;\r\n      &lt;/a&gt;\r\n      &lt;ul class=&quot;dropdown-menu&quot; role=&quot;menu&quot; aria-labelledby=&quot;myTabDrop1&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#jmeter&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; data-toggle=&quot;tab&quot;&gt;\r\n            jmeter&lt;/a&gt;\r\n         &lt;/li&gt;\r\n         &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#ejb&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; data-toggle=&quot;tab&quot;&gt;\r\n            ejb&lt;/a&gt;\r\n         &lt;/li&gt;\r\n      &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n   &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;myTabContent&quot; class=&quot;tab-content&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane fade in active&quot; id=&quot;home&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;p&gt;W3Cschoool菜鸟教程是一个提供最新的web技术站点，本站免费提供了建站相关的技术文档，帮助广大web技术爱好者快速入门并建立自己的网站。菜鸟先飞早入行——学的不仅是技术，更是梦想。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane fade&quot; id=&quot;ios&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;p&gt;iOS 是一个由苹果公司开发和发布的手机操作系统。最初是于 2007 年首次发布 iPhone、iPod Touch 和 Apple \r\n      TV。iOS 派生自 OS X，它们共享 Darwin 基础。OS X 操作系统是用在苹果电脑上，iOS 是苹果的移动版本。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane fade&quot; id=&quot;jmeter&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;p&gt;jMeter 是一款开源的测试软件。它是 100% 纯 Java 应用程序，用于负载和性能测试。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane fade&quot; id=&quot;ejb&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;p&gt;Enterprise Java Beans（EJB）是一个创建高度可扩展性和强大企业级应用程序的开发架构，部署在兼容应用程序服务器（比如 JBOSS、Web Logic 等）的 J2EE 上。\r\n      &lt;/p&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;script&gt;\r\n   $(function () {\r\n      $(&#39;#myTab li:eq(1) a&#39;).tab(&#39;show&#39;);\r\n   });\r\n&lt;/script&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p><br/></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结果如下所示：</p><div class=\"cover\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/tabpluginmethods_demo.jpg\" alt=\"标签页（Tab）插件方法\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></div><h2 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 2px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.8em; line-height: 1.8em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">事件</h2><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下表列出了标签页（Tab）插件中要用到的事件。这些事件可在函数中当钩子使用。</p><table class=\"reference notranslate\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 4px 0px; padding: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; width: 729px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><tbody style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><tr style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 240);\"><th style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(85, 85, 85); margin: 0px; padding: 3px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: top; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">事件</th><th style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(85, 85, 85); margin: 0px; padding: 3px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: top; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">描述</th><th style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(85, 85, 85); margin: 0px; padding: 3px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); vertical-align: top; text-align: left; background-color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">实例</th></tr><tr style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\">show.bs.tab</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\">该事件在标签页显示时触发，但是必须在新标签页被显示之前。分别使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>event.target</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>和<strong>event.relatedTarget</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>来定位到激活的标签页和前一个激活的标签页。</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\"><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">$(&#39;a[data-toggle=&quot;tab&quot;]&#39;).on(&#39;show.bs.tab&#39;, function (e) {\r\n  e.target // 激活的标签页\r\n  e.relatedTarget // 前一个激活的标签页\r\n})</pre></td></tr><tr style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 240);\"><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\">shown.bs.tab</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\">该事件在标签页显示时触发，但是必须在某个标签页已经显示之后。分别使用<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span><strong>event.target</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>和<strong>event.relatedTarget</strong><span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>来定位到激活的标签页和前一个激活的标签页。</td><td style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(212, 212, 212); margin: 0px; padding: 7px 5px; font-size: 1em; vertical-align: top;\"><pre class=\"prettyprint\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">$(&#39;a[data-toggle=&quot;tab&quot;]&#39;).on(&#39;shown.bs.tab&#39;, function (e) {\r\n  e.target // 激活的标签页\r\n  e.relatedTarget // 前一个激活的标签页\r\n})</pre></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 8px 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 1.4em; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">实例</h3><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下面的实例演示了标签页（Tab）插件事件的用法。在本实例中，将显示当前和前一个访问过的标签页：</p><pre class=\"prettyprint tryit\" style=\"border-width: 1px 1px 1px 4px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); margin: 15px auto; padding: 10px 15px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: &#39;courier new&#39;; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.runoob.com/images/codecolorer_bg.gif) 50% 0% rgb(251, 251, 251);\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;\r\n&lt;html&gt;\r\n&lt;head&gt;\r\n   &lt;title&gt;Bootstrap 实例 - 标签页（Tab）插件事件&lt;/title&gt;\r\n   &lt;link href=&quot;/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css&quot; rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;/scripts/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n   &lt;script src=&quot;/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;\r\n&lt;/head&gt;\r\n&lt;body&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;hr&gt;\r\n   &lt;p class=&quot;active-tab&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;激活的标签页&lt;/strong&gt;：&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n   &lt;p class=&quot;previous-tab&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;前一个激活的标签页&lt;/strong&gt;：&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;hr&gt;\r\n&lt;ul id=&quot;myTab&quot; class=&quot;nav nav-tabs&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;li class=&quot;active&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#home&quot; data-toggle=&quot;tab&quot;&gt;\r\n      W3Cschool Home&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n   &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#ios&quot; data-toggle=&quot;tab&quot;&gt;iOS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n   &lt;li class=&quot;dropdown&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;a href=&quot;#&quot; id=&quot;myTabDrop1&quot; class=&quot;dropdown-toggle&quot; \r\n         data-toggle=&quot;dropdown&quot;&gt;\r\n         Java &lt;b class=&quot;caret&quot;&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n      &lt;ul class=&quot;dropdown-menu&quot; role=&quot;menu&quot; aria-labelledby=&quot;myTabDrop1&quot;&gt;\r\n         &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#jmeter&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; data-toggle=&quot;tab&quot;&gt;jmeter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n         &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#ejb&quot; tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; data-toggle=&quot;tab&quot;&gt;ejb&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n      &lt;/ul&gt;\r\n   &lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;myTabContent&quot; class=&quot;tab-content&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane fade in active&quot; id=&quot;home&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;p&gt;W3Cschoool菜鸟教程是一个提供最新的web技术站点，本站免费提供了建站相关的技术文档，帮助广大web技术爱好者快速入门并建立自己的网站。菜鸟先飞早入行——学的不仅是技术，更是梦想。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane fade&quot; id=&quot;ios&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;p&gt;iOS 是一个由苹果公司开发和发布的手机操作系统。最初是于 2007 年首次发布 iPhone、iPod Touch 和 Apple \r\n      TV。iOS 派生自 OS X，它们共享 Darwin 基础。OS X 操作系统是用在苹果电脑上，iOS 是苹果的移动版本。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane fade&quot; id=&quot;jmeter&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;p&gt;jMeter 是一款开源的测试软件。它是 100% 纯 Java 应用程序，用于负载和性能测试。&lt;/p&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n   &lt;div class=&quot;tab-pane fade&quot; id=&quot;ejb&quot;&gt;\r\n      &lt;p&gt;Enterprise Java Beans（EJB）是一个创建高度可扩展性和强大企业级应用程序的开发架构，部署在兼容应用程序服务器（比如 JBOSS、Web Logic 等）的 J2EE 上。\r\n      &lt;/p&gt;\r\n   &lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;script&gt;\r\n   $(function(){\r\n      $(&#39;a[data-toggle=&quot;tab&quot;]&#39;).on(&#39;shown.bs.tab&#39;, function (e) {\r\n      // 获取已激活的标签页的名称\r\n      var activeTab = $(e.target).text(); \r\n      // 获取前一个激活的标签页的名称\r\n      var previousTab = $(e.relatedTarget).text(); \r\n      $(&quot;.active-tab span&quot;).html(activeTab);\r\n      $(&quot;.previous-tab span&quot;).html(previousTab);\r\n   });\r\n});\r\n&lt;/script&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/body&gt;\r\n&lt;/html&gt;</pre><p><br/></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; font-size: 12px; font-family: &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">结果如下所示：</p><div class=\"cover\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(214, 214, 214); margin: 0px; padding: 5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"http://www.runoob.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/tabpluginevents_demo.jpg\" alt=\"标签页（Tab）插件事件\" style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"/></div><p><br/></p><p></p><p></p><p></p>'),(58,'<p></p><p></p><p></p><h1 style=\"border: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-size: 2.1em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; font-family: &#39;Open Sans&#39;, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, Arial, STHeiti, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-v